      "bibliographie": "<p><span class=\"TextRun SCXW211748105 BCX8\" lang=\"EN-US\" xml:lang=\"EN-US\" data-contrast=\"auto\"><span class=\"NormalTextRun SpellingErrorV2Themed SCXW211748105 BCX8\">Folien</span><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW211748105 BCX8\">, Handout</span></span> &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</p>",
